---
// TrustCredentials.astro
// Centralized business credentials block — update here, updates everywhere.
---

<section
    class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white border-t border-gray-100"
>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-14">
            <span
                class="text-orange-500 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm"
                >Why Homeowners Trust Us</span
            >
            <h2
                class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mt-2 mb-4"
            >
                Credentials That Matter
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">
                We believe trust is built on transparency—not taglines. Here are
                the specifics behind our commitment to every homeowner we serve.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
            <!-- Insurance -->
            <div
                class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                    $1 Million Liability Policy
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Every project is backed by a comprehensive $1,000,000
                    general liability insurance policy. Your property and our
                    work are fully protected—no exceptions, no gaps.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Years in Business -->
            <div
                class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-14 h-14 bg-green-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-7 h-7 text-green-600"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                    7 Years in Business
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Seven years of serving North Alabama homeowners. That is
                    more than 2,500 days of earned experience, refined
                    technique, and accumulated knowledge about how homes in this
                    region actually perform.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Certified Carpenter -->
            <div
                class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-14 h-14 bg-orange-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-7 h-7 text-orange-600"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                    Certified Carpenter
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Not just a handyman—a certified carpenter. Structural
                    understanding, joinery knowledge, and finish-level precision
                    on every project, from crown molding to complete room
                    framing.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Family Owned -->
            <div
                class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-14 h-14 bg-rose-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-7 h-7 text-rose-600"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                    Family Owned & Operated
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    This is not a franchise. There is no corporate office in
                    another state. We are a family-owned business rooted in
                    North Alabama. When you call, you reach the people who
                    actually do the work.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Service Guarantee -->
            <div
                class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-14 h-14 bg-emerald-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-7 h-7 text-emerald-600"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                    Work Warranty & Satisfaction Guarantee
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    We warranty every project we complete. If something is not
                    functioning correctly or you are not satisfied with the
                    result, we come back and make it right—no arguments, no
                    runaround, no charge. The job is not finished until you say
                    it is.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Response Time -->
            <div
                class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-14 h-14 bg-indigo-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-7 h-7 text-indigo-600"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                    3-Hour Response Promise
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Every voicemail and text message receives a reply within
                    three hours during business hours. You will never wonder
                    whether we received your message. Communication is not
                    optional—it is the foundation of how we operate.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Summary bar -->
        <div class="bg-blue-900 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 text-white">
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-6 text-center">
                <div>
                    <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold">$1M</p>
                    <p class="text-blue-200 text-sm mt-1">Liability Coverage</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold">7</p>
                    <p class="text-blue-200 text-sm mt-1">Years in Business</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold">Certified</p>
                    <p class="text-blue-200 text-sm mt-1">Carpenter</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold">Family</p>
                    <p class="text-blue-200 text-sm mt-1">Owned & Operated</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold">100%</p>
                    <p class="text-blue-200 text-sm mt-1">Work Warranty</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold">
                        &lt; 3 hrs
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-blue-200 text-sm mt-1">Response Time</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
